<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Elite Defense Dojo ‚Äì Tang Soo Do</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no, viewport-fit=cover">
    <style>
        :root { 
            --gold: #facc15; 
            --bg: #020617; 
            --card: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8); 
            --accent: #38bdf8; 
            --text: #f8fafc;
        }
        body { 
            margin: 0; 
            background: var(--bg); 
            font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; 
            color: var(--text); 
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Mockup Header */
        .dojo-header {
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 30px 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.1), transparent);
        }
        .kanji { font-size: 3rem; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px var(--gold)); }
        .dojo-title { font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0; }
        .subtitle { color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; }

        .section-title { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1rem; margin: 25px 0 15px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        /* Training Grid */
        .training-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .step-card {
            background: #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 3px solid var(--gold);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .step-num { 
            background: #1e293b; color: white; padding: 4px 10px; 
            border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: bold; 
            align-self: flex-start; margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .step-img { width: 70px; height: 70px; margin-bottom: 15px; object-fit: contain; }
        .step-txt { color: #0f172a; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 900; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1.2; }

        /* Master's Box */
        .sensei-box {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 20px 20px 0;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .sensei-box b { color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }

        .finish-btn {
            width: 100%; padding: 20px; border-radius: 20px; border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #facc15, #eab308);
            color: black; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 40px; cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="dojo-header">
        <span class="kanji">ÈÅìÂ†¥</span>
        <h1 class="dojo-title">ELITE DEFENSE DOJO</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Tang Soo Do Principles</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">Technique: Palm Heel Strike</div>
    <div class="training-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">STEP 1</div>
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3565/3565910.png" class="step-img">
            <div class="step-txt">Chamber Position</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">STEP 2</div>
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/10539/10539958.png" class="step-img">
            <div class="step-txt">Open Palm Strike</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">STEP 3</div>
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3663/3663335.png" class="step-img">
            <div class="step-txt">Ki-hap & Distance</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">STEP 4</div>
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5555/5555133.png" class="step-img">
            <div class="step-txt">Active Defense</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sensei-box">
        <b>ü•ã SENSEI'S SECRET (2ND DAN TIP):</b>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.4;">
            In Tang Soo Do, power comes from the hip rotation (Hur Ri Ro). Don't just push with your arm‚Äîtwist your waist to maximize the impact.
        </p>
    </div>

    <button class="finish-btn" onclick="location.href='index.html'">COMPLETE LESSON</button>

</body>
</html>
 